[
  {
    "text": " ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=2"
  },
  {
    "text": "Hi. I'm Eryn Wells, an engineer ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=9"
  },
  {
    "text": "on the Authentication Experience Team. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=11"
  },
  {
    "text": "If your app or website ever asks someone for a password, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=14"
  },
  {
    "text": "then you know that account security ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=17"
  },
  {
    "text": "is critically important. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=19"
  },
  {
    "text": "In this video, I'm gonna talk about ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=20"
  },
  {
    "text": "how to keep your customer's accounts more secure ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=23"
  },
  {
    "text": "and how to make signing in with verification codes ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=26"
  },
  {
    "text": "even easier with the new verification code generator ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=28"
  },
  {
    "text": "built into iCloud Keychain.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=31"
  },
  {
    "text": "This is a big topic, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=33"
  },
  {
    "text": "and I'm gonna break it down into three important parts. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=35"
  },
  {
    "text": "First, we'll talk about passwords, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=39"
  },
  {
    "text": "some of the security problems they have, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=42"
  },
  {
    "text": "and how multistep authentication ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=44"
  },
  {
    "text": "helps address some of those problems. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=46"
  },
  {
    "text": "Second, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=49"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'll talk about time-based verification codes, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=50"
  },
  {
    "text": "including a brand-new authenticator ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=53"
  },
  {
    "text": "we've built into iCloud Keychain ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=56"
  },
  {
    "text": "in iOS 15 and macOS Monterey. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=57"
  },
  {
    "text": "Finally, I'll take a step back ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=62"
  },
  {
    "text": "to discuss the beginning of a big change ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=64"
  },
  {
    "text": "happening in the world of authentication, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=66"
  },
  {
    "text": "as well as some other opportunities ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=69"
  },
  {
    "text": "to improve how people sign in with verification codes.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=70"
  },
  {
    "text": "OK, let's talk about passwords and multistep authentication.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=76"
  },
  {
    "text": "Passwords are everywhere, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=81"
  },
  {
    "text": "and people understand how to use them. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=83"
  },
  {
    "text": "However, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=86"
  },
  {
    "text": "it turns out they're difficult to use correctly. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=87"
  },
  {
    "text": "In fact, it's easier to misuse passwords ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=90"
  },
  {
    "text": "than to use them correctly. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=93"
  },
  {
    "text": "People frequently reuse passwords ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=95"
  },
  {
    "text": "across multiple websites ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=97"
  },
  {
    "text": "or choose passwords that are easy to guess. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=99"
  },
  {
    "text": "It's also pretty easy for an attacker ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=102"
  },
  {
    "text": "to convince someone to give up their password. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=104"
  },
  {
    "text": "So services are faced with a dilemma: ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=107"
  },
  {
    "text": "How do we add security to our users' accounts ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=110"
  },
  {
    "text": "while still making it easy to log in? ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=112"
  },
  {
    "text": "Many services add steps to their log-in flows. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=116"
  },
  {
    "text": "They ask for additional pieces of information ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=120"
  },
  {
    "text": "to confirm someone's identity. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=122"
  },
  {
    "text": "Adding steps like this reduces the chance ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=125"
  },
  {
    "text": "that an attacker with someone's password ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=127"
  },
  {
    "text": "will be able to access that person's account. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=129"
  },
  {
    "text": "It also means the attacker won't automatically have access ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=132"
  },
  {
    "text": "to any other accounts ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=136"
  },
  {
    "text": "where that person used the same password. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=138"
  },
  {
    "text": "Verification codes are a common additional step. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=141"
  },
  {
    "text": "Services ask for these codes ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=144"
  },
  {
    "text": "after someone has entered their user name and password. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=146"
  },
  {
    "text": "These codes are either delivered over SMS, email, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=148"
  },
  {
    "text": "or a push notification, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=152"
  },
  {
    "text": "or they're generated by an authenticator app ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=154"
  },
  {
    "text": "on the person's phone ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=157"
  },
  {
    "text": "or with a hardware key fob.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=158"
  },
  {
    "text": "An essential feature of these codes ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=161"
  },
  {
    "text": "is that they're single use. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=163"
  },
  {
    "text": "Since they're not intended to be memorized or stored, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=165"
  },
  {
    "text": "they're not susceptible to reuse like passwords are. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=168"
  },
  {
    "text": "Verification codes do still require a human ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=172"
  },
  {
    "text": "to enter the code, though, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=174"
  },
  {
    "text": "so they're still prone to phishing ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=176"
  },
  {
    "text": "in the same way that passwords are. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=177"
  },
  {
    "text": "The most common way by far ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=179"
  },
  {
    "text": "that verification codes are delivered is with SMS. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=181"
  },
  {
    "text": "Almost everyone who has a cell phone ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=185"
  },
  {
    "text": "can receive a text message, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=187"
  },
  {
    "text": "and people understand sending and receiving texts.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=189"
  },
  {
    "text": "AutoFill made it even easier to use these codes. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=193"
  },
  {
    "text": "Just one tap fills a code into any text field. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=196"
  },
  {
    "text": "But there are still real problems ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=200"
  },
  {
    "text": "with verification codes delivered over SMS. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=202"
  },
  {
    "text": "For one thing, they're not very secure. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=205"
  },
  {
    "text": "They're vulnerable to snooping on carrier networks ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=208"
  },
  {
    "text": "and SIM-swapping attacks, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=210"
  },
  {
    "text": "where an attacker can receive messages ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=212"
  },
  {
    "text": "meant for someone else.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=214"
  },
  {
    "text": "People tend to take for granted ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=217"
  },
  {
    "text": "that text messages will come and go without error, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=219"
  },
  {
    "text": "but they do require network access. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=222"
  },
  {
    "text": "So if someone's on an airplane or away from strong service, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=224"
  },
  {
    "text": "it might take a long time for a message to arrive ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=228"
  },
  {
    "text": "or it may not arrive at all.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=231"
  },
  {
    "text": "Finally, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=235"
  },
  {
    "text": "SMS messages have a cost, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=236"
  },
  {
    "text": "both to send and to receive. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=238"
  },
  {
    "text": "So sending millions of these messages ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=240"
  },
  {
    "text": "can really add up. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=242"
  },
  {
    "text": "Another way verification codes are done ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=244"
  },
  {
    "text": "is with on-device code generators. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=246"
  },
  {
    "text": "The algorithm for doing this is defined in RFC 6238 ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=249"
  },
  {
    "text": "and is called \"Time-Based One-Time Passwords,\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=253"
  },
  {
    "text": "or \"TOTP.\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=256"
  },
  {
    "text": "It takes a secret key and a time ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=258"
  },
  {
    "text": "and produces a short numeric code ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=261"
  },
  {
    "text": "based on those bits of information. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=263"
  },
  {
    "text": "Typically, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=265"
  },
  {
    "text": "an authenticator app or hardware device ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=266"
  },
  {
    "text": "generates the codes. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=268"
  },
  {
    "text": "It doesn't require any communication with the service. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=270"
  },
  {
    "text": "It all happens on the device.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=273"
  },
  {
    "text": "This is a huge benefit in terms of security and user experience. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=276"
  },
  {
    "text": "Codes are valid for a short amount of time, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=280"
  },
  {
    "text": "typically 30 seconds or so. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=284"
  },
  {
    "text": "And it results in lower costs ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=286"
  },
  {
    "text": "for both services and customers ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=288"
  },
  {
    "text": "because no one has to send or receive SMS messages.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=290"
  },
  {
    "text": "The challenge with TOTP ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=295"
  },
  {
    "text": "is that it tends to be a bit more complicated to set up. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=297"
  },
  {
    "text": "Services have to share a secret key ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=301"
  },
  {
    "text": "with their customers, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=303"
  },
  {
    "text": "along with several other parameters, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=304"
  },
  {
    "text": "so that the customer's device can start generating codes. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=307"
  },
  {
    "text": "A typical setup process involves displaying a QR code ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=310"
  },
  {
    "text": "on one device, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=314"
  },
  {
    "text": "downloading an authenticator app on another device, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=315"
  },
  {
    "text": "and then scanning the QR code with that app. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=318"
  },
  {
    "text": "This is a cumbersome process, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=321"
  },
  {
    "text": "and it's difficult to explain to people. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=322"
  },
  {
    "text": "Generating codes on-device is a better experience ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=325"
  },
  {
    "text": "for everyone, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=328"
  },
  {
    "text": "but it does still have some pesky issues around setup. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=329"
  },
  {
    "text": "We took a careful look at some of those difficulties ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=332"
  },
  {
    "text": "and developed a new feature of iCloud Keychain ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=335"
  },
  {
    "text": "that brings a streamlined setup experience ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=338"
  },
  {
    "text": "together with AutoFill ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=340"
  },
  {
    "text": "into something really fantastic.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=342"
  },
  {
    "text": "New in iOS 15 ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=345"
  },
  {
    "text": "and macOS Monterey, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=347"
  },
  {
    "text": "we've built time-based verification code generators ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=349"
  },
  {
    "text": "into iCloud Keychain Password Manager, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=352"
  },
  {
    "text": "and I am so excited to show you how this works.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=354"
  },
  {
    "text": "We started with the basics: ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=358"
  },
  {
    "text": "looking up and copying codes ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=360"
  },
  {
    "text": "to use on this device or another device. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=362"
  },
  {
    "text": "These are important features of any authenticator app.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=365"
  },
  {
    "text": "But AutoFill really makes this shine. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=369"
  },
  {
    "text": "Just like with codes delivered over SMS, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=373"
  },
  {
    "text": "AutoFill fills generated verification codes ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=376"
  },
  {
    "text": "with a single tap. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=379"
  },
  {
    "text": "Because codes are immediately available, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=381"
  },
  {
    "text": "your customers get a more streamlined, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=383"
  },
  {
    "text": "reliable sign-in experience, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=385"
  },
  {
    "text": "and you get to reduce the costs of sending SMS messages.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=387"
  },
  {
    "text": "One of my favorite parts of this feature ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=391"
  },
  {
    "text": "is how easy it can be to set up a new verification code. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=394"
  },
  {
    "text": "When you add a special link or a button ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=398"
  },
  {
    "text": "to your TOTP setup pages, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=400"
  },
  {
    "text": "someone using iOS 15 or macOS Monterey ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=402"
  },
  {
    "text": "will be able to set up a new verification code ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=405"
  },
  {
    "text": "on the same device with just a couple taps. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=408"
  },
  {
    "text": "It's really, really easy.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=410"
  },
  {
    "text": "Finally, verification codes are synced ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=414"
  },
  {
    "text": "across all of a person's devices, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=416"
  },
  {
    "text": "and they're securely backed up with iCloud Keychain. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=419"
  },
  {
    "text": "So they don't have to pull out their iPhone ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=422"
  },
  {
    "text": "to fill a verification code ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=425"
  },
  {
    "text": "when they're signing in to an account on their Mac. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=426"
  },
  {
    "text": "This is great for account recovery too. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=428"
  },
  {
    "text": "When verification codes are safely backed up in iCloud, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=431"
  },
  {
    "text": "losing a device no longer means losing access to accounts. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=434"
  },
  {
    "text": "As a reminder, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=439"
  },
  {
    "text": "everything in iCloud Keychain is end-to-end encrypted, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=440"
  },
  {
    "text": "so no one except the owner of the account-- ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=444"
  },
  {
    "text": "not Apple or anyone else-- ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=447"
  },
  {
    "text": "can access them.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=449"
  },
  {
    "text": "Devices with iCloud Keychain enabled ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=453"
  },
  {
    "text": "are protected by Face ID, Touch ID, or a passcode. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=455"
  },
  {
    "text": "And every Apple device has the highest level of security ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=460"
  },
  {
    "text": "supported by the operating system. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=463"
  },
  {
    "text": "So Keychain data is safe, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=465"
  },
  {
    "text": "no matter which device a person has in the moment. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=467"
  },
  {
    "text": "Apple's Platform Security Guide describes all of this ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=471"
  },
  {
    "text": "and a lot more in great detail.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=474"
  },
  {
    "text": "There are a few easy things you can do ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=479"
  },
  {
    "text": "to ensure your customers have the best possible experience ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=481"
  },
  {
    "text": "setting up and filling codes. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=484"
  },
  {
    "text": "For your setup flows, there are two things, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=486"
  },
  {
    "text": "and for your log-in flows, there's just one. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=488"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's talk a little about each one.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=490"
  },
  {
    "text": "Being able to set up a new verification code ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=493"
  },
  {
    "text": "with just a few taps is a big deal. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=496"
  },
  {
    "text": "Hundreds of millions of iPhone users ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=499"
  },
  {
    "text": "are going to be able to do this ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=501"
  },
  {
    "text": "as soon as they update to iOS 15. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=502"
  },
  {
    "text": "You can make it super easy ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=505"
  },
  {
    "text": "to set up verification codes on their devices ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=506"
  },
  {
    "text": "by adding a link or a button ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=509"
  },
  {
    "text": "that does this to your setup screens.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=511"
  },
  {
    "text": "If you already have infrastructure ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=515"
  },
  {
    "text": "to support logging in with TOTP codes, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=516"
  },
  {
    "text": "you might be familiar with otpauth: URLs. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=519"
  },
  {
    "text": "These URLs contain all of the information required ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=522"
  },
  {
    "text": "to set up a code generator, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=525"
  },
  {
    "text": "including the base32-encoded secret key, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=527"
  },
  {
    "text": "the number of digits in each code, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=532"
  },
  {
    "text": "the period of time that each code is valid for, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=535"
  },
  {
    "text": "and an issuer field ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=539"
  },
  {
    "text": "that you should set to your domain name. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=541"
  },
  {
    "text": "iCloud Keychain uses this field to suggest an account ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=543"
  },
  {
    "text": "to add the verification code to.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=546"
  },
  {
    "text": "This is the same URL that you encode into the QR codes ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=549"
  },
  {
    "text": "that are a common part of the TOTP setup process. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=553"
  },
  {
    "text": "You can link directly ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=557"
  },
  {
    "text": "to the iCloud Keychain Password Manager ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=558"
  },
  {
    "text": "by prefixing the URL with \"apple-\".",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=561"
  },
  {
    "text": "You can take this apple otpauth: URL ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=565"
  },
  {
    "text": "and put it in an anchor tag on your web page. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=568"
  },
  {
    "text": "And in apps, you have two options. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=572"
  },
  {
    "text": "You can create a link by adding the \"link\" attribute ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=574"
  },
  {
    "text": "to an NSAttributedString ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=576"
  },
  {
    "text": "that you assign to a textView's attributedString property, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=578"
  },
  {
    "text": "or you can open the URL in response to a button tap ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=582"
  },
  {
    "text": "with the open API on the window scene. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=586"
  },
  {
    "text": "You can check ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=589"
  },
  {
    "text": "whether the system can open apple otpauth: URLs ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=590"
  },
  {
    "text": "with an availability check. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=593"
  },
  {
    "text": "On previous versions of iOS, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=595"
  },
  {
    "text": "you should hide setup buttons and remove setup URLs.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=597"
  },
  {
    "text": "The second thing you can do during setup ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=602"
  },
  {
    "text": "is to use raster images like JPGs, PNGs, or GIFs ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=604"
  },
  {
    "text": "for QR codes intended to be scanned by other TOTP apps. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=608"
  },
  {
    "text": "Safari uses on-device image analysis ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=612"
  },
  {
    "text": "to detect QR codes ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=615"
  },
  {
    "text": "and decode the information they contain. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=616"
  },
  {
    "text": "If Safari determines ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=619"
  },
  {
    "text": "that the QR code contains an otpauth: URL, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=620"
  },
  {
    "text": "it will offer to set up the code generator ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=624"
  },
  {
    "text": "in the context menu for the QR code image.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=626"
  },
  {
    "text": "The last thing to do concerns text fields ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=630"
  },
  {
    "text": "for entering generated codes. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=632"
  },
  {
    "text": "To ensure that AutoFill knows ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=635"
  },
  {
    "text": "exactly where to fill user names, passwords, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=637"
  },
  {
    "text": "and verification codes, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=639"
  },
  {
    "text": "annotate those text fields with content types. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=641"
  },
  {
    "text": "You can do this in SwiftUI ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=644"
  },
  {
    "text": "with the textContentType view modifier, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=646"
  },
  {
    "text": "in UIKit with the textContentType property ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=649"
  },
  {
    "text": "on UITextFields, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=652"
  },
  {
    "text": "in AppKit apps with the contentType property ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=654"
  },
  {
    "text": "on NSTextFields, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=657"
  },
  {
    "text": "and on the web, you can set the auto-complete attribute ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=658"
  },
  {
    "text": "to \"one-time-code\" on input elements. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=661"
  },
  {
    "text": "So now, I wanna take a step back. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=665"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's look at the big picture of authentication ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=667"
  },
  {
    "text": "and talk a little about ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=670"
  },
  {
    "text": "how to make your existing infrastructure more secure.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=671"
  },
  {
    "text": "Authentication mechanisms exist on a spectrum, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=676"
  },
  {
    "text": "increasing in strength and security as you move along. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=678"
  },
  {
    "text": "Passwords are the traditional baseline ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=682"
  },
  {
    "text": "for the industry, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=684"
  },
  {
    "text": "and there are a number of ways ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=686"
  },
  {
    "text": "that services reinforce password-based log-in flows. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=687"
  },
  {
    "text": "Two of the most common are Passwords + Codes ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=691"
  },
  {
    "text": "delivered over SMS ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=694"
  },
  {
    "text": "and Passwords + Codes generated with TOTP.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=696"
  },
  {
    "text": "An additional decision services make ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=702"
  },
  {
    "text": "is whether to use a federated sign-in provider ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=704"
  },
  {
    "text": "that delegates the entire process of authentication ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=706"
  },
  {
    "text": "to another service. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=709"
  },
  {
    "text": "Federated authentication options are based ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=711"
  },
  {
    "text": "on all the same mechanisms as traditional methods ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=714"
  },
  {
    "text": "but require people to keep track of fewer passwords. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=717"
  },
  {
    "text": "When implemented on robust, secure infrastructure-- ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=720"
  },
  {
    "text": "as is the case with Sign in with Apple-- ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=724"
  },
  {
    "text": "they can also be more secure ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=726"
  },
  {
    "text": "than those traditional mechanisms.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=728"
  },
  {
    "text": "A step beyond any of these ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=732"
  },
  {
    "text": "is to get rid of passwords altogether. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=734"
  },
  {
    "text": "The WebAuthentication standard, or \"WebAuthn,\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=736"
  },
  {
    "text": "does exactly this. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=739"
  },
  {
    "text": "Instead, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=741"
  },
  {
    "text": "it uses public key cryptography to keep accounts safe. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=742"
  },
  {
    "text": "iOS 15 and macOS Monterey contain a preview ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=746"
  },
  {
    "text": "of this technology ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=749"
  },
  {
    "text": "that offers a usable replacement for passwords. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=751"
  },
  {
    "text": "My teammate Garrett has a video about it ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=754"
  },
  {
    "text": "that you should definitely check out.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=757"
  },
  {
    "text": "As our whole industry continues to work ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=759"
  },
  {
    "text": "on building that future without passwords, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=762"
  },
  {
    "text": "there is still real value ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=764"
  },
  {
    "text": "in taking steps to improve the security ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=765"
  },
  {
    "text": "of the infrastructure you already have ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=767"
  },
  {
    "text": "and may continue to have for a while. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=770"
  },
  {
    "text": "Anything you can do to keep people safer online is good.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=773"
  },
  {
    "text": "One step you can take concerns verification codes ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=779"
  },
  {
    "text": "delivered over SMS. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=781"
  },
  {
    "text": "As you're evaluating adopting time-based verification codes, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=783"
  },
  {
    "text": "you might still need to send codes with SMS.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=787"
  },
  {
    "text": "In iOS 14 and macOS Big Sur, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=791"
  },
  {
    "text": "we introduced a simple mechanism ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=794"
  },
  {
    "text": "for making your SMS codes more resistant to phishing ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=795"
  },
  {
    "text": "by adding domain bindings to your messages. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=799"
  },
  {
    "text": "A domain binding is a way of communicating with AutoFill ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=802"
  },
  {
    "text": "that the code in this message is meant for a particular domain. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=806"
  },
  {
    "text": "When the code is bound in this way, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=810"
  },
  {
    "text": "AutoFill will only offer the code ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=812"
  },
  {
    "text": "if the domain it's bound to ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=814"
  },
  {
    "text": "matches the domain of the web page ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=816"
  },
  {
    "text": "or one of your app's associated domains. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=818"
  },
  {
    "text": "In apps, this works on the same mechanisms ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=821"
  },
  {
    "text": "as associated domains and universal links. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=824"
  },
  {
    "text": "So if you've already configured your apps ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=827"
  },
  {
    "text": "for those technologies, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=829"
  },
  {
    "text": "you're all set to add domain bindings.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=830"
  },
  {
    "text": "You can learn more about this in an article we published ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=833"
  },
  {
    "text": "about enhancing the security of SMS codes with domain bindings.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=836"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now that you know all about verification codes, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=841"
  },
  {
    "text": "go and do these two important things. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=843"
  },
  {
    "text": "First, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=846"
  },
  {
    "text": "adopt time-based verification codes ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=847"
  },
  {
    "text": "in your apps and websites. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=849"
  },
  {
    "text": "Add support to your back ends, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=851"
  },
  {
    "text": "and encourage your customers to use them ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=852"
  },
  {
    "text": "instead of getting codes over SMS. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=854"
  },
  {
    "text": "Second, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=856"
  },
  {
    "text": "if you are continuing to support SMS verification codes, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=857"
  },
  {
    "text": "add domain bindings to your messages.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=861"
  },
  {
    "text": "Thank you for watching. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=864"
  },
  {
    "text": "[music]",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10105/?time=865"
  }
]